                <head>37. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d37fn1">Source: Carter Library, <persName
                            corresp="#p_BZK_1">Brzezinski</persName> Donated Material, Subject File,
                        Box 31, [Meetings—<gloss target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> 228: 12/13/79].
                        Secret. The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room. The
                        minutes are not attached and were not found. <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1"
                            >Carter</persName> wrote “Zbig J” in the upper right-hand corner of the
                        first page.</note>
                </head>
